https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/appc-labs-server/downloads/Hyperloop+for+Android+Programming+Guide.pdf

HyperLoop does a pretty good job in allowing you to use Java with Javascript syntax, but that doesn't mean that you won't
need to learn Java if you want to customise the module / create your own. Take your time and look up Java tutorials on youtube
if you find



