This module was tested and developed with the following environment:
- Titanium SDK 6.0.0.v20161017194738
- HyperLoop 2.0.0

We included a full project within this zip so you can quickly build and run it.
The only thing you need to do is make sure that the GUID value in the TiApp.XML is valid, or copy all the properties defined in the provided TiApp.xml to an
existing one.



